				"cell_type": "markdown",
				"metadata": {
					"nteract": {
						"transient": {
							"deleting": false
						}
					}
				},
				"source": [
					"Could potentially have multiple steps to the logic, by putting multiple statements in the sql file, then breaking those up in spark. You could make temp sql tables between each step and then reference them in the next"
